description:
Fast and free online prototyping tool for web and app projects

Mockplus RP is a web-based prototyping tool that allows users to create everything from sketches and wireframes to high-fidelity prototypes. It supports a wide range of visual designs, including web and mobile app artboards, and offers vector tools for detailed customization. Users can drag-and-drop premade shapes and widgets to create interactive prototypes, which can be tested and shared easily. The tool also supports real-time team collaboration and allows importing Axure files for seamless editing and feedback collection.
